description: If you're looking for food just like your mama used to make, you won't find anything better than what you'll get from Mama Duke's Catering!This is some serious feel-good food that's sure to put a smile on your face. From their Pulled Pork Sandwich to their Chicken Tenders to their hand-prepped Catfish, anything and everything you order will leave you supremely satisfied. Stop by for a tasty bite from the best home-cooked food around!
name: Mama Duke's Catering
